data.meta_description: Edmund Frantow was born on May 29, 1888 in Pontianak, Borneo, West-Kalimantan, Indonesië, son of Albert Wilhelm Frans Frantow and Waniekem... He died on August  8, 1957 in Terneuzen, Zeeland, Netherlands. This information is part of Family tree Torn by Murphy Torn on Genealogy Online.
